          resonates deeply with this city's professional culture: communicate
          clearly, execute precisely, and let the work speak for itself. We do
          not oversell. We do not show up in a branded truck playing a jingle.
          We show up in clean uniforms, assess the situation honestly, provide a
          written estimate that will not change, complete the work on schedule,
          and clean up when we are finished. In Huntsville—a city that literally
          puts rockets into space—anything less would be an insult to the
          standard your community has set.
